{"data": {"repository": {"pullRequest": {"id": "MDExOlB1bGxSZXF1ZXN0MzY0OTU4NDMy", "number": 4496, "title": "Issue 4495: Recording WARN and ERROR log entries as metrics.", "bodyText": "Change log description\n\nRecording all WARNs and ERRORs as metrics with logging class name and exception name as tags.\n\nPurpose of the change\nFixes #4495.\nWhat the code does\n\nCreated a new Log Appender to intercept all log entries that have severity set to WARN or ERROR.\nAll these are reported into metrics via 2 distinct counters (one for WARN, one for ERROR), and using the source class/log name as a tag, and exception name (if any) as another tag.\n\nHow to verify it\nUnit tests updated. A longevity with metrics should also be run to verify this.", "createdAt": "2020-01-20T18:30:49Z", "url": "https://github.com/pravega/pravega/pull/4496", "merged": true, "mergeCommit": {"oid": "40b38f44c1621c03c09b5ffbb1103eccedcb07f3"}, "closed": true, "closedAt": "2020-01-21T22:47:50Z", "author": {"login": "andreipaduroiu"}, "timelineItems": {"totalCount": 6, "pageInfo": {"startCursor": "Y3Vyc29yOnYyOpPPAAABb8Q2bbgH2gAyMzY0OTU4NDMyOjRiNDVjMTliZjU2ZmUzMWFlYTNhMjQyNGI1MzEyMGQzNTc2M2NjYmY=", "endCursor": "Y3Vyc29yOnYyOpPPAAABb8nl-tAH2gAyMzY0OTU4NDMyOjQ0MmQ1ODQwY2U2NmEzN2JhOWNlZTNiZGIyYjQ4ZjI2MjliOGJiODE=", "hasNextPage": false, "hasPreviousPage": false}, "nodes": [{"__typename": "PullRequestCommit", "commit": {"oid": "4b45c19bf56fe31aea3a2424b53120d35763ccbf", "author": {"user": {"login": "andreipaduroiu", "name": "Andrei Paduroiu"}}, "url": "https://github.com/pravega/pravega/commit/4b45c19bf56fe31aea3a2424b53120d35763ccbf", "committedDate": "2020-01-20T18:28:19Z", "message": "Recording all WARNs and ERRORs as metrics with class name as a tag.\n\nSigned-off-by: Andrei Paduroiu <andrei.paduroiu@dell.com>"}}, {"__typename": "PullRequestReview", "id": "MDE3OlB1bGxSZXF1ZXN0UmV2aWV3MzQ1NTAwOTQx", "url": "https://github.com/pravega/pravega/pull/4496#pullrequestreview-345500941", "createdAt": "2020-